data.description: Welcome to this stunning single family home nestled in a prime location, offering convenience and leisure at every turn. This beautiful property sits near various interstates, making your daily commute a breeze. Imagine waking up to the incredible view of a brand new Rivers Casino and golf course right across the street, providing entertainment and recreation just a stone's throw away! This community boasts fantastic amenities, including a refreshing pool and a well-equipped clubhouse gym, perfect for staying active and socializing with neighbors. Not to mention, having your own driveway allows you to park your car hassle-free, eliminating the need for street parking. With 2 living levels and custom kitchen with granite counter tops, this townhome offers a lifestyle of comfort and convenience that's hard to resist with its ideal blend of accessibility and leisure. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to make it your dream home!
